divs: Sighting DetailsI took a photo where only weeks ago a large object had been captured on video hovering over the Carlton Gardens in Melbourne, Australia. I could not see anything with my naked eye at the time, however when reviewing the photo I observed a dark sphere to my surprise!
Summary: Dark Orb over Carlton Gardens - Daylight Event
